This paper is about developing neural network image classification models, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning and architecture engineering, which are topics commonly studied in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper proposes a new search space for neural network architecture, which is a topic related to neural networks (cs.NE) and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
